				<font face="verdana" size="2" color="black">
				Just a real quick note. Make sure that if you are a Ranger that you are always useing your &quot;Sense heading&quot; skill. I have found that this skill is invaluable when it comes to hunting in West Karana. When you are leading a group around the plains all you have to do is sense your heading and figure out which way is west and then you can find your way right back to the Q hills. Its that simple. However this skill goes up very slowly and is very hard to remember to keep using it due to the failure rate. I am level 10 ranger and i have a skill lvl of over 50 on Sense heading and i still fail about 2 out of 5 times.<BR>
